==About==
===Format===
* '''Group Stage:''' ''July 10th - 11th''
** 64 teams: divided into 4 groups.
** 6 matches each day.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 12 teams}} from each group advance to ''Quarter Finals''.
<div style=margin-top:1em></div>
* '''Quarter Finals:''' ''July 12th - 14th''
** 48 teams: divided into 3 groups.
** 6 matches each day.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} from each group advance to ''Semi Finals''.
<div style=margin-top:1em></div>
* '''Semi Finals:''' ''July 15th - 17th''
** 24 teams: divided into 3 groups.
** 6 matches each day.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 16 teams}} advance to ''Finals''.
<div style=margin-top:1em></div>
* '''Grand Finals:''' ''July 18th - 20th''
** 16 teams.
** 6 matches each day.

